content: Can someone contact the administrator to the Harris website? They keep posting messages that they need someone from the campaign to contact them. Message gets bigger every day. Here is what the Home page looks like when you try to buy a T-shirt.
Do you happen to have the URL this message is at?
Hi there!  I'm not sure who owns that URL, but this is the official Harris website store here: https://store.kamalaharris.com/
You can find official t-shirts and other merch!
So weird - the url I shared forwards to kamalaharris.com
Just because something forwards does not mean its official. I would avoid that site

That appears to be someone outside the campaign who owns the domain harriswalz.com. They'd probably like to sell it to the campaign, since according to news reports, they spent $15k to buy the domain. It's nice that they're at least forwarding to the official site, for now.
If we're talking about fake sites (And that's what I came here to do) I'm assuming this is false and not a dime goes to the campaign
LuckyBeity may or may not donate all their profits to the campaign, If you want to make sure your money goes where it should use https://kamalaharris.com
The problem is, that could change instantly
It's likely that the campaign has grabbed all the possible URLs that someone would try, and the campaign is providing the redirecting.
